Package: 18650-battery-test
Version: 1.0.0
Section: test-applications
Architecture: windows_all
Depends: ni-python (>= 3.10)
Maintainer: NI Test Engineering <test-eng@ni.com>
XB-Plugin: file
XB-UserVisible: yes
Description: 18650 Battery Test — SystemLink-integrated test application
 Functional/parametric test for 18650 Li-ion battery cells.
 Measures open circuit voltage, voltage under load, internal resistance,
 capacity, charge/discharge voltage, weight, and temperature.
 Reports results to SystemLink Test Monitor with full step-level data.
Homepage: https://github.com/ni/notebook-examples
